features: Triangular tip for hair-like strokes and fool-proof brows

Insta-worthy. Fill in and define your brows with our unique triangular pencil tip. It creates strokes small enough to look like your finest hairs and sharpens the edges of those brows with rub-resistant pigments. Brush and blend it all out with the pencil's built-in spoolie. When you’re done, the tip retracts for quick-and-easy storage in your makeup bag.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Make Up For Play EVERYBODY’S FIRST wet n wild has made budget beauty accessible to mass audiences since 1979. We reinvent the meaning of value with high-performance essentials and new innovations, in clean, cruelty-free products. wet n wild gives people the freedom to choose – from award-winning eyeliners, to foundations championed by beauty influencers and makeup artists as outperforming luxury products! 100% Cruelty Free wet n wild NEVER tests on animals. We are proud members of PETA’s “Beauty Without Bunnies” program, which is committed to eradicating animal testing. We believe in cruelty-free beauty first! None of our furry, feathery, or scaly friends would ever be used for product testing.

FACE Your skin, made better! Our vitamin-packed primers, flawless high-coverage foundations and concealers, velvety powders, and hydrating natural perfectors deliver ultimate value and performance. EYE For smoking, popping, shaping, or for ultimate smudge-proof precision, our liners, eyeshadows, mascaras and brow products are absolute essentials for your makeup arsenal. LIP High-gloss moisture, budge-proof mattes, metallics, and deeply nourishing treatments in every shade and finish you could ask for. NAIL We love being your first! Our nail polish is legendary for value, and we continue to offer high-performance innovation in a range of shades and effects for any occasion.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I like this eyebrow pencil very much. It is easy to use and goes on well. I like the pencil lead shape angel which is different, and it is not hard like some other pencils. It goes on with ease. I could do without the brush on the other end, as I would rather have more lead as I have a few brushes from days gone by. The color I use suits me perfect.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Favorite for the cost
reviews.reviewText: Love the cost, love the angle of the pencil, stays well easy to use perfect coloring

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Far better than anything else I have tried and a fraction of the price.
reviews.reviewText: This is the best eyebrow pencil I have used in many years. There used to be one from Estée Lauder that I loved, but they changed the formula. Ever since, and that’s been many years, I have looked for a replacement. This is it.The color is good and can be modified and lightened with the brush at the other end of the pencil.You can make a thin line or fill-in with bolder strokes.The price is fantastic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cheap and does a good job
reviews.reviewText: I have to fill in my eyebrows daily and use/ have used many different ( more expensive) pencils. This is great to always have on hand for just everyday or when I run out. It's really great for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars No so good
reviews.reviewText: I got this from reading all the positive reviews. I thought it was going to be a sharper tip. It’s actually quite thick. When applying it doesn’t stay up you have to keep turning it back up. So that didn’t make sense. For me it’s a no.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You can't even tell!
reviews.reviewText: This pencil has become my daily eyebrow essential. It's reliable and gets the job done effortlessly.Consistent and Realistic Color: The color is consistent, and it genuinely looks realistic. No awkward surprises – just natural-looking brows.No Issues: Seriously, no problems here. It glides on smoothly without any hiccups.Dual-Sided Brow Brush: The dual-sided brush is a nice touch for added convenience. Everything I need in one tool.If you want an eyebrow pencil that not only performs well but also gives you that natural and consistent look, this one's a winner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I LOOOOVE this product. I've only had to buy one and its been like two years (its been a while at least), it still has some left in it. It is not too dark and matches exactly with my eyebrow color. It is a great texture. Best eyebrow makeup i've had. Super easy to use. Easy to fix if you mess up. Comes with brush on the other end. Perfection!
Eine feine Mine garantiert das gute Ergebnis....
It’s been my favourite for years now. Looks so natural and absolutely smudge proof!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on November 20, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Nice colour and doesn't rub off easilyThe tip is also a good shape, goes on nicely and no need to keep sharpening it :)Nice size aswell as you don't need to press down hard or use much so I imagine it will last a decent amount of daily use
